  "instructions": [
    "Cook jasmine rice according to package instructions.",
    "Grill or saut\u00059 the chicken breast until cooked through, then chop into bite-sized pieces.",
    "In a pan, heat coconut oil over medium heat.",
    "Add red curry paste and cook for 1-2 minutes, until fragrant.",
    "Add enchilada sauce, fish sauce, lime juice, and grated ginger. Stir to combine.",
    "Add chopped chicken and sliced red chilies to the sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for 2-3 minutes, until the sauce has thickened slightly.",
    "Fluff cooked jasmine rice with a fork and divide among bowls.",
    "Top with the spicy chicken mixture, sliced green onions, and a sprinkle of chili flakes if desired.",
    " Garnish with fresh cilantro."
